<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="unfair-adj">unfair <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌʌn'feə(r)/    美 /ˌʌn'fer/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>不公平的；不正当的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 fair </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>unfair treatment 
不公平的待遇</p><footer>2009 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It seems <strong>unfair on</strong> / to him to make him pay for everything.<strong>to_1</strong>
让他承担一切费用似乎对他不公平。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>by unfair means 
用不正当的手段</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>unfairly /ˌʌn'feə(r)li/ adv <br />
unfairness /ˌʌn'feə(r)nes/ n   </p></div>